sn_aia_tool.description:
This skill takes in short descriptions from multiple records from the GAIC Defect table. It Analyzes and finds meaningful patterns from the short descriptions and groups those defect records numbers to the buckets. Create distinct bucket names and assign each defect number to a bucket based on the nature of the issue

Respond in JSON format as follows:
{
     &#34;buckets&#34;: {
          &#34;Bucket Name 1&#34;: [&#34;DEF001&#34;, &#34;DEF002&#34;],
          &#34;Bucket Name 2&#34;: [&#34;DEF003&#34;],
          &#34;Bucket Name 3&#34;: [&#34;DEF004&#34;, &#34;DEF005&#34;],
      }
}
